Commentary Text: Tushar Deshpande to Prithvi Shaw, out Caught by Rayudu!! In the airrr, young Rayudu takes a flying catch. Full and in the slot, this is clearly a shot forced towards mid-off because of the man pushed back to long-on prior to this ball. Looks like it was Tushar's call to ask Dhoni for that field. Well done. So a slot ball, had mid-on been in, it was an easy loft over the infield straight or on the leg-side. Because long-on was placed, Shaw tried to open his bat face slightly to go over mid-off. Hit it fairly straight, but Rayudu moves to his right and judged it perfectly. Shaw stands there and wonders how he hit that to hand. Prithvi Shaw c Rayudu b Tushar Deshpande 5(7) [4s-1]
